OPNsense SIEM-Lite Plugin
=========================

Lightweight Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) built directly into
OPNsense. Provides real-time log correlation, Sigma rule-based threat detection,
security dashboards, incident timeline, and alerting — all without external
dependencies.

Features:
- Multi-source log ingestion (firewall, IDS/IPS, proxy, VPN, auth, system)
- Sigma rule engine for standardised threat detection
- Event correlation with configurable time windows
- Security dashboard with geo-map, top threats, risk score
- Incident timeline and investigation workflow
- Alert management with severity levels and notification channels
- Compliance-ready audit trail and reporting
- Built-in rule library with automatic updates

